author: China Insights-SOHTV
description:
#Iran #nuclear #worldwar3 
Think China just makes phones and tea? Think again. The Chinese Communist Party is busy running the world’s most dangerous nuclear “gift shop,” handing out bomb-making kits to Iran, North Korea, Pakistan — like it’s a clearance sale. Join us as we hilariously expose how Beijing’s nuclear generosity is anything but friendly, turning the planet into one big ticking time bomb. Spoiler: This isn’t your typical holiday giveaway.
title: CCP’s Nuclear ‘Friendship’ Program: Spoiler, It’s Not Friendly
